into the later degrees of
Libra about three weeks.

00:09:25.457 --> 00:09:26.540 align:middle line:90%
>> BECVAR: That's correct.

00:09:26.540 --> 00:09:28.490 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So if everyone's
looking at their chart roughly,

00:09:28.490 --> 00:09:30.350 align:middle line:84%
if you in your
mind can calculate,

00:09:30.350 --> 00:09:31.950 align:middle line:90%
slide it back about three weeks.

