but we're in the cusp phase.

00:15:20.220 --> 00:15:21.352 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: OK.

00:15:21.352 --> 00:15:24.790 align:middle line:84%
>> BECVAR: And because of
that, we're starting to feel

00:15:24.790 --> 00:15:26.170 align:middle line:90%
the shift.

00:15:26.170 --> 00:15:29.930 align:middle line:84%
We're starting to feel the
influence of this new period.

