we're approaching

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:38.380 align:middle line:84%
a shift, an astrological
shift, our attention is

00:15:38.380 --> 00:15:42.440 align:middle line:84%
on that new territory and we're
starting to think more about it,

00:15:42.440 --> 00:15:44.710 align:middle line:84%
and we're feeling some
of the influence of that.

00:15:44.710 --> 00:15:49.520 align:middle line:84%
So because of this shift that
