a lot of the old forms
are breaking down.

00:15:52.070 --> 00:15:55.190 align:middle line:84%
The old governmental forms,
the old religious forms,

00:15:55.190 --> 00:15:57.410 align:middle line:84%
the old economic forms,
the old social forms,

