is about making this shift
into this new consciousness.

00:16:48.325 --> 00:16:49.640 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: I think so.

00:16:49.640 --> 00:16:51.930 align:middle line:84%
>> BECVAR: All of the people
that you've talked with,

00:16:51.930 --> 00:16:54.530 align:middle line:84%
