are feeling it and are open--

00:17:08.779 --> 00:17:09.079 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah, excited.

00:17:09.079 --> 00:17:10.412 align:middle line:90%
>> BECVAR: --to that transition.

00:17:10.412 --> 00:17:11.339 align:middle line:90%
Excited, yeah.

00:17:11.339 --> 00:17:14.569 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I mean, for me, that
pendulum of time that swings

