into Kali Yuga, the lead age.

00:18:03.650 --> 00:18:05.560 align:middle line:90%
And we have come out of that.

00:18:05.560 --> 00:18:08.178 align:middle line:84%
Like in the 1600s, we've begun
to come out of Kali Yuga.

00:18:08.178 --> 00:18:09.220 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: The Kali Yuga.

00:18:09.220 --> 00:18:11.213 align:middle line:84%
>> BECVAR: Yeah, it
was such a dark time.

00:18:11.213 --> 00:18:12.380 align:middle line:90%
We won't even talk about it.

00:18:12.380 --> 00:18:13.505 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah, let's not.

00:18:13.505 --> 00:18:17.650 align:middle line:84%
>> BECVAR: But we're now in the
upward moving period of Dvapara

00:18:17.650 --> 00:18:21.730 align:middle line:84%
Yuga, which is reflected in all
the technological developments.

00:18:21.730 --> 00:18:25.630 align:middle line:84%
