00:29:43.460 --> 00:29:46.250 align:middle line:84%
and avarice or give
rise to addiction

00:29:46.250 --> 00:29:49.295 align:middle line:90%
in terms of the kama principle.

00:29:49.295 --> 00:29:51.000 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Let me understand.

