of these, the moral values,

00:29:54.030 --> 00:29:56.330 align:middle line:84%
economic values, psychological
values, spiritual values

00:29:56.330 --> 00:29:58.500 align:middle line:90%
are all playing in our chart.

00:29:58.500 --> 00:30:00.390 align:middle line:90%
They're playing all the time.

00:30:00.390 --> 00:30:04.600 align:middle line:84%
But depending on our
birth and our rising sign,

