person's rising sign

00:32:07.270 --> 00:32:12.340 align:middle line:84%
in complementary
relationship to that,

00:32:12.340 --> 00:32:15.383 align:middle line:90%
is it opposite for one thing?

00:32:15.383 --> 00:32:16.300 align:middle line:90%
That can be very good.

