Or is it the same?

00:32:17.200 --> 00:32:18.190 align:middle line:90%
That can be very good.

00:32:18.190 --> 00:32:20.940 align:middle line:84%
Or is it the same or a
complementary element?

00:32:20.940 --> 00:32:22.840 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Element, right.

00:32:22.840 --> 00:32:26.200 align:middle line:84%
So in that sense, Western
astrology is similar.

00:32:26.200 --> 00:32:27.210 align:middle line:90%
>> BECVAR: Yeah.

