when somebody's--

00:33:47.190 --> 00:33:50.630 align:middle line:84%
There's a whole lot that goes
into arranging a marriage,

00:33:50.630 --> 00:33:51.720 align:middle line:90%
making a decision.

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:54.090 align:middle line:84%
It's changed somewhat
for modern Indians.

00:33:54.090 --> 00:33:57.180 align:middle line:84%
But this idea of
utilizing the moon signs

00:33:57.180 --> 00:33:58.270 align:middle line:90%
can really be helpful.

00:33:58.270 --> 00:33:59.770 align:middle line:84%
Because the moon,
as I said earlier,

00:33:59.770 --> 00:34:01.780 align:middle line:84%
it has to do with the
manas, the intuitive mind.

00:34:01.780 --> 00:34:04.197 align:middle line:84%
