But we also look at the
positions of Venus, for example.

00:34:21.190 --> 00:34:24.870 align:middle line:84%
The Venus positions have a lot
to do with the things we love

00:34:24.870 --> 00:34:27.000 align:middle line:90%
and enjoy and are attracted to.

00:34:27.000 --> 00:34:29.050 align:middle line:84%
So the Venus positions
are harmonious.

