that because they just

00:34:40.260 --> 00:34:41.679 align:middle line:90%
feel good with each other.

00:34:41.679 --> 00:34:44.210 align:middle line:84%
They don't even know why,
they just want to snuggle up.

00:34:44.210 --> 00:34:45.010 align:middle line:90%
They fall in love.

00:34:45.010 --> 00:34:45.843 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Hang out.

00:34:45.843 --> 00:34:49.139 align:middle line:84%
>> BECVAR: Hang out, it's
a very important component.

00:34:49.139 --> 00:34:52.239 align:middle line:84%
Also, the sun signs, of
course, come into play.

00:34:52.239 --> 00:34:54.589 align:middle line:84%
And Jupiter, the position
of Jupiter-- actually,

00:34:54.589 --> 00:34:55.389 align:middle line:90%
all the planets.

00:34:55.389 --> 00:34:57.750 align:middle line:84%
But there are some
cornerstone elements

00:34:57.750 --> 00:35:00.910 align:middle line:84%
that I always look at in
compatibility analysis.

00:35:00.910 --> 00:35:04.300 align:middle line:84%
And believe me, over the 30
odd years I've been doing this,

00:35:04.300 --> 00:35:06.443 align:middle line:84%
I rarely see it that
it doesn't work.

00:35:06.443 --> 00:35:08.110 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It doesn't
play out that way.

00:35:08.110 --> 00:35:10.210 align:middle line:84%
>> BECVAR: I mean, there are
many different combinations,

00:35:10.210 --> 00:35:10.660 align:middle line:90%
obviously.

00:35:10.660 --> 00:35:12.660 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes somebody will
be attracted to somebody

00:35:12.660 --> 00:35:15.023 align:middle line:84%
because Venus is good and
you just fall in love.

00:35:15.023 --> 00:35:16.690 align:middle line:84%
But the moon signs
might not be so good,

00:35:16.690 --> 00:35:18.670 align:middle line:84%
so their communications
might be wonky.

00:35:18.670 --> 00:35:20.945 align:middle line:84%
So that's where they need
to do some adjustments.

00:35:20.945 --> 00:35:23.310 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yeah, what do you
do when you're working with

00:35:23.310 --> 00:35:26.970 align:middle line:84%
a couple that's looking at their
compatibility in a chart and you

00:35:26.970 --> 00:35:29.486 align:middle line:90%
see some breathtaking obstacles.

00:35:29.486 --> 00:35:31.370 align:middle line:90%
>> BECVAR: Well, I do.

00:35:31.370 --> 00:35:32.170 align:middle line:90%
It happens.

00:35:32.170 --> 00:35:36.300 align:middle line:84%
And believe me, one very
good tool I'll tell you

00:35:36.300 --> 00:35:39.000 align:middle line:84%
right now because it's useful
for anybody and anybody could do

00:35:39.000 --> 00:35:41.790 align:middle line:84%
it even with their partner or
with the clerk in the grocery

00:35:41.790 --> 00:35:45.660 align:middle line:84%
store, is to inquire of
yourself from time to time,

00:35:45.660 --> 00:35:49.300 align:middle line:84%
in this moment, in this moment,
whatever this moment is,

00:35:49.300 --> 00:35:53.020 align:middle line:84%
what would nourishment be
like for this other person?

00:35:53.020 --> 00:35:56.193 align:middle line:84%
And just suspend your
own agenda, whatever

00:35:56.193 --> 00:35:57.610 align:middle line:84%
that is, and just
inquire, what is

00:35:57.610 --> 00:36:00.580 align:middle line:84%
nourishment like in this
moment for this other person?

00:36:00.580 --> 00:36:03.320 align:middle line:84%
And let yourself get a
little intuitive hit.

00:36:03.320 --> 00:36:06.550 align:middle line:84%
You'll get a little message
if you ask that sincerely.

00:36:06.550 --> 00:36:08.770 align:middle line:84%
You might get a
message like, well, it

00:36:08.770 --> 00:36:11.513 align:middle line:84%
might be nourishing for
this person to take a walk,

00:36:11.513 --> 00:36:13.430 align:middle line:84%
or it be nourishing for
them to watch a movie,

00:36:13.430 --> 00:36:15.260 align:middle line:84%
or it might be
nourishing for them to--

00:36:15.260 --> 00:36:16.910 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what, could
be a million things.

00:36:16.910 --> 00:36:18.660 align:middle line:84%
